lead_paragraph: Tennessee Tech is picked to finish second in its division of the Ohio Valley Conference, and coach Steve Payne is hopeful that a fifth-year transfer from Tulane will help put the Golden Eagles over the top.

headline.print_headline: Fifth-Year Transfers Threaten Low- and Mid-Majors
